 invaluable experience in dive education and operations while working at various dive resorts before founding DiveWorx in 2005, a dive and travel tours company that rapidly expanded to include motor boats and a comprehensive range of diving equipment.</p><p class="z-[2] max-w-[700px] sm:ml-[25%] sm:text-lg md:ml-[40%] lg:ml-[50%]">Actively participating in dive shows across Asia and the U.S., Glenn continues to broaden Azure’s presence in the international and local diving community. He leads the Negros Oriental Dive Resorts Association as the 3rd time President. Committed to providing world-class service, Azure reflects Glenn’s dedication and vision for excellence in the diving industry.</p><img src="<?php echo THEME_URI ?>/media/topographic-2.svg" alt="" class="absolute right-[-40%] z-[1] h-auto w-[100%] -translate-y-[60%] rotate-180 object-cover object-center opacity-10 sm:right-[-40%] sm:top-[-50%] sm:size-[100%] sm:translate-y-0 sm:object-contain"/></div><div class="relative -mx-8 grid grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] items-end gap-10 sm:mb-[-256px] sm:translate-y-[-256px] sm:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr_3fr] sm:gap-18 sm:pr-18"><img src="<?php echo THEME_URI ?>/media/dive/history-1.jpg" alt="" class="hidden h-[calc(min(400px,var(--h-screen-noheader))+200px)] w-full rounded-tr-[120px] object-cover object-center sm:block sm:h-[calc(min(600px,var(--h-screen-noheader))+200px)]"/><img src="<?php echo THEME_URI ?>/media/dive/history-2.jpg" alt="" class="h-[min(400px,var(--h-screen-noheader))] w-full rounded-tr-[120px] object-cover object-center sm:h-[min(600px,var(--h-screen-noheader))]"/><img src="<?php echo THEME_URI ?>/media/dive/history-3.jpg" alt="" class="h-[calc(min(400px,var(--h-screen-noheader))-200px)] w-full object-cover object-center sm:h-[calc(min(600px,var(--h-screen-noheader))-200px)] sm:rounded-tr-[120px]"/></div></section><section class="relative bg-pale-blue px-8 py-25 sm:p-25"><div class="z-[2] mx-auto max-w-content"><p class="mb-4 text-overline-big sm:mb-5 sm:text-over